      "content": "it's not just the silence. it's the fact that i'm just going through the motions for no reason. waking up, eating, working... it's all so pointless without him. i feel like i'm just dragging this heavy, broken version of myself around every single day. i just want the weight to stop. i just want everything to be still.",
